OL,3,CLifeguards could have deterred death
OL,4,Cof teenager who jumped from pier
OL,6,FLifeguards at the beach where a
OL,7,Fteenager died after jumping from a
OL,8,Fpier could have prevented his death,
OL,9,Fan inquest has found.
OL,11,FDavid Ejimofor, 15, died on June 19,
OL,12,F2023, after jumping into the water at
OL,13,FAberavon's small beach from the pier
OL,14,Fwhile celebrating the end of his GCSE
OL,15,Fexams.
