OL,3,CLifeguards could have deterred death
OL,4,Cof teenager who jumped from pier
OL,6,FThe court heard that lifeguard hours
OL,7,Fhad been scaled back at Aberavon beach
OL,8,Fyears before David's death. A
OL,9,Flifeguard manager said cover at the
OL,10,Fbeach ended at 6 pm - David died
OL,11,Fshortly after 7 pm.
OL,13,FThe court heard that if manned, a
OL,14,Flifeguard could have reached David
OL,15,Fquickly.
OL,17,FThe Coroner Edward Ramsey said David's
OL,18,Fswimming ability would also have been
OL,19,Fa factor in his death, that's despite
OL,20,Fhim having swimming lessons as a child.
