OL,3,CLifeguards could have deterred death
OL,4,Cof teenager who jumped from pier
OL,6,FThe court had previously heard David
OL,7,Fwas not a strong swimmer and was
OL,8,Fnervous about jumping from the pier,
OL,9,Ftelling a group of friends before
OL,10,Fjumping that he couldn't swim.
OL,12,FCoroner Ramsey also noted the impact
OL,13,Fof cold water shock and panic after
OL,14,Fjumping from a height into the sea
OL,15,Fcould also have had an impact on
OL,16,FDavid's ability to swim. The coroner
OL,17,Fdescribed the jump as an inherently
OL,18,Frisky activity.
