OL,6,FA prevention of future deaths report -
OL,7,Fwhich is compiled by the coroner to
OL,8,Frelevant authorities to address
OL,9,Fconcerns - will now be produced
OL,11,FFollowing the inquest, the RNLI
OL,12,Freleased a statement which read: "Our
OL,13,Fthoughts and sincere condolences go
OL,14,Fout to the family and friends of
OL,15,FDavid. As a charity, we exist to
OL,16,Fprevent drowning so that nobody
OL,17,Fsuffers the devastating loss of a
OL,18,Floved one in this way.
