OL,3,CLifeguards could have deterred death
OL,4,Cof teenager who jumped from pier
OL,6,F"The RNLI works closely with Councils
OL,7,Fand landowners to determine when the
OL,8,Fcharity will provide lifeguard
OL,9,Fpatrols. RNLI lifeguard patrols
OL,10,Froutinely operate between the hours of
OL,11,F10am-6pm, because this is the time
OL,12,Fperiod which incident data tells us is
OL,13,Fthe busiest and highest risk period."
